{"tid":2275461,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不得不承認，香港選特首制度比美國大選公正得多","createTime":"2020-11-07T07:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T21:12:46.000Z","uid":250308,"like":7,"dislike":83,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4fbe00c39c7060c32b01bfa0bcd4787d0d2e7a0a","tid":2275461,"uid":250308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:31:44.000Z","msg":"起碼選委會有代表性，只要選委會成員係由民選公投出黎，咁就非常接近民意<br />\n<br />\n而美國大選亂七八糟，好多隆liu野，55波既洲明明民意55波，只要輸個馬鼻，大拿拿幾十票就比q晒一邊，反映到個個州既民意咩？ 變相就只係一個遊戲，比你用一d手段去扭曲到成個選舉核心價值。香港人太妄自菲薄，明明好多野比美國有過之而無不及，但就崇洋媚外既關係搞到成日內亂，不就是傻的嗎"},{"pid":"5a5ccf944dd11b5c6ac67ccf09a1930b4f19731f","tid":2275461,"uid":152476,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:32:40.000Z","msg":"On撚9"},{"pid":"f62ea183fd66b03d6108178c09ff56e9e8f19d80","tid":2275461,"uid":154054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:36:54.000Z","msg":"其實呢個問題好多美國人自己都有講<br />\n例如侵粉係加州知道投左都冇用會索性玩野投俾birthday party <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />中間個d州大部份係撐侵既，民主黨支持者又係投都懶得投<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b639e4936cb98ce48cbcb2f7bc484867b071c073","tid":2275461,"uid":326280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"香港特首選舉得1200張票 點比啊大佬"},{"pid":"db2a816622abf36e891b02b343caaee7d3b13d05","tid":2275461,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b639e4936cb98ce48cbcb2f7bc484867b071c073","tid":2275461,"uid":326280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T07:46:21.000Z","msg":"香港特首選舉得1200張票 點比啊大佬"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T08:30:45.000Z","msg":"如果可以普選嗰1200條友又唔同講法嘅"},{"pid":"15ddae15e78c7462a8d0217eacc50118de11d676","tid":2275461,"uid":313839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db2a816622abf36e891b02b343caaee7d3b13d05","tid":2275461,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b639e4936cb98ce48cbcb2f7bc484867b071c073","tid":2275461,"uid":